sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Visitor
    participant Browser as Public Site UI
    participant App as Next.js App Router
    participant Validation as Zod Validation
    participant API as API Route / Server Action
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)
    participant Admin as Dashboard User

    Visitor->>Browser: Fill contact form (name, email, subject, message)
    Browser->>App: Submit form payload
    App->>Validation: Validate payload schema

    alt Invalid payload
        Validation-->>App: Validation errors
        App-->>Browser: Return field errors
        Browser-->>Visitor: Show inline validation feedback
    else Valid payload
        Validation-->>App: Sanitized input
        App->>API: Create message
        API->>DB: INSERT into MESSAGE
        DB-->>API: Message ID + timestamps

        opt User checks newsletter opt-in
            App->>API: Upsert subscriber(email, source)
            API->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE SUBSCRIBER
            DB-->>API: Subscriber status
        end

        API-->>App: Success response
        App-->>Browser: Confirmation state
        Browser-->>Visitor: "Message sent" feedback

        Admin->>App: Open dashboard messages
        App->>API: Fetch unread list
        API->>DB: SELECT * FROM MESSAGE WHERE isRead=false
        DB-->>API: Message rows
        API-->>App: Message previews
        App-->>Admin: Render inbox cards
    end